    "---\n",
    "## 1. Problem Statement & Motivation <a id='1-problem-statement'></a>\n",
    "\n",
    "### The Global Healthcare Access Crisis\n",
    "\n",
    "The World Health Organization estimates a global shortfall of **15 million health workers**, with the gap concentrated almost entirely in low- and middle-income countries. Over **4.5 billion people** — more than half the world's population — lack access to basic primary healthcare.\n",
    "\n",
    "In rural Pakistan, sub-Saharan Africa, and remote Southeast Asia:\n",
    "- The nearest clinic may be **3–6 hours away**\n",
    "- Community Health Workers (CHWs) with minimal clinical training are often the **only** first responder\n",
    "- Misclassifying an emergency as non-urgent (or vice versa) can be **fatal**\n",
    "\n",
    "### The Gap MediSense Fills\n",
    "\n",
    "A CHW standing in front of a patient with chest pain and shortness of breath needs to know: *Is this urgent? Should this person travel three hours to a hospital right now, or rest at home?*\n",
    "\n",
    "**MediSense AI** provides that answer in under 90 seconds — with clinical reasoning, red flags, and actionable next steps — using only a browser and an internet connection.\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "Without MediSense          With MediSense\n",
    "─────────────────          ──────────────\n",
    "CHW guesses urgency   →    AI-structured triage in <90 seconds\n",
    "Patient waits hours   →    Immediate guidance with red flags\n",
    "No follow-up path     →    Conversational Q&A for clarification\n",
    "No documentation      →    Structured JSON output for records\n",
    "```\n"
   ]
  },

