   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "arch-md",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## 9. Architecture Overview <a id='9-architecture'></a>\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n",
    "│                        USER INTERFACE                           │\n",
    "│  Single HTML File (No server · No install · Browser only)       │\n",
    "│                                                                 │\n",
    "│  ┌─────────────────┐    ┌──────────────────┐    ┌───────────┐  │\n",
    "│  │  Patient Intake  │    │  Symptom Tags +  │    │ Severity  │  │\n",
    "│  │  Age/Sex/History │    │  Free Text Input │    │  Slider   │  │\n",
    "│  └────────┬─────────┘    └────────┬─────────┘    └─────┬─────┘  │\n",
    "│           └──────────────────────┴──────────────────────┘       │\n",
    "│                                  │                              │\n",
    "│                     Structured Clinical Prompt                   │\n",
    "└──────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────┘\n",
    "                                   │  HTTPS API Call\n",
    "                                   ▼\n",
    "              ┌──────────────────────────────────────┐\n",
    "              │         GROQ INFERENCE API            │\n",
    "              │    llama-3.3-70b-versatile            │\n",
    "              │    ~750 tokens/sec · <3s latency      │\n",
    "              └──────────────────────┬───────────────┘\n",
    "                                     │  JSON Response\n",
    "                                     ▼\n",
    "              ┌──────────────────────────────────────┐\n",
    "              │          RESPONSE PARSER              │\n",
    "              │  Validates JSON schema                │\n",
    "              │  Maps to TriageResult dataclass       │\n",
    "              └──────────────────────┬───────────────┘\n",
    "                                     │\n",
    "                    ┌────────────────┴─────────────────┐\n",
    "                    ▼                                  ▼\n",
    "         ┌─────────────────────┐           ┌──────────────────────┐\n",
    "         │   TRIAGE RESULT UI  │           │  FOLLOW-UP CHAT      │\n",
    "         │  • Urgency level    │           │  • Full context kept  │\n",
    "         │  • Clinical summary │           │  • Multi-turn Q&A    │\n",
    "         │  • Red flags        │           │  • Empathetic tone   │\n",
    "         │  • Next steps       │           └──────────────────────┘\n",
    "         │  • Conditions list  │\n",
    "         └─────────────────────┘\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "### Key Design Decisions\n",
    "\n",
    "| Layer | Technology | Why |\n",
    "|---|---|---|\n",
    "| Frontend | Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS | Zero dependencies, works offline (except API call), shareable via WhatsApp |\n",
    "| LLM | LLaMA 3.3 70B | Best open model for medical reasoning; Groq delivers sub-second inference |\n",
    "| Output | Strict JSON schema | Typed, parseable, consistent; never relies on regex extraction |\n",
    "| Safety | Conservative bias + disclaimers | False negatives (missed emergencies) are worse than false positives |\n",
    "| Privacy | Stateless (no data stored) | No patient data persisted; each session is ephemeral |\n"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "ethics-md",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## 10. Ethical Considerations & Limitations <a id='10-ethics'></a>\n",
    "\n",
    "### ⚠️ What MediSense Is NOT\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Not a medical device.** It does not replace clinical judgment.\n",
    "- **Not a diagnostic tool.** It identifies possible conditions to *consider*, not confirmed diagnoses.\n",
    "- **Not a treatment recommendation engine.** Steps are guidance, not prescriptions.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Known Limitations\n",
    "\n",
    "| Limitation | Impact | Mitigation |\n",
    "|---|---|---|\n",
    "| LLM hallucination | Model may suggest plausible but incorrect conditions | Conservative bias; always show red flags |\n",
    "| Training data bias | LLaMA 3.3 trained mostly on English medical literature; may underrepresent regional disease patterns | Future: fine-tune on WHO essential medicines data |\n",
    "| No objective vitals | No temperature, BP, or O2 readings | Future: integrate Bluetooth medical peripherals |\n",
    "| Connectivity required | Groq API call needs internet | Future: embed quantized model (Gemma 4 E2B) for offline use |\n",
    "| Language barrier | English-only currently | Future: multilingual support (Urdu, Swahili, Hindi) |\n",
    "\n",
    "### Ethical Safeguards Built In\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **Persistent disclaimers** — every result explicitly labeled \"Preliminary AI Analysis\"\n",
    "2. **Conservative escalation** — system prompt instructs \"when in doubt, escalate\"\n",
    "3. **Explainable outputs** — shows *why* a level was assigned, not just the level\n",
    "4. **No data retention** — zero patient information stored anywhere\n",
    "5. **Transparent limitations** — conditions list phrased as \"possible\" not \"confirmed\"\n"
   ]
  },

